# CS2 Server Picker Linux - Todo List

# Base Api: https://api.steampowered.com/ISteamApps/GetSDRConfig/v1/?appid=730

## Core Features
- [X] Get server list from the API
function: get_server_info()
- [X] Get ip and port from the server list
- [X] Get server details
- [X] User interface for displaying server list
- [ ] Search functionality for server list
- [ ] Button for refreshing, block all, unblock all
- [ ] Button for block selected
- [X] Use iptable to temporarily block servers 

## Optional Features
- [ ] Import and export config
- [ ] Save blocked servers to a file
- [ ] Make a deb package for easy installation

